OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid in Scotland: Care    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstaff can get booster      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F'without losing wages'     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Social care staff who attend vaccine   
OL,6, appointments during working hours will 
OL,7, not need to lose wages, the Scottish   
OL,8, government has said.                   
OL,10,FHealth Secretary Humza Yousaf said     
OL,11,Fbooster uptake was lower among social  
OL,12,Fcare workers than other sectors.       
OL,14,FHe said a booster was "crucial" for    
OL,15,Fstaff working with vulnerable people.  
OL,17,FFinancial support will be given to     
OL,18,Femployers so staff can receive booster 
OL,19,Fjabs without having to sacrifice paid  
OL,20,Fhours or annual leave days.            
